rd repeatable practices across the theatres. This team will drive internal and external communities to expand the knowledge and use of best practices. This team will also partner with Services PLM to drive standard offer components that are repeatable and standardized. Your Responsibilities Develop, deploy, and measure Architectural Best Practice by Platform (BPO, BPI, ROA, UAA) Lead the DevOps Exchange / Communities globally Lead Communities across Customer Success (PM, Business Analyst, Consultants/Engineers, etc.) Standardize processes across Customer Success Team Review program deliverables and harvest standard developments for re-use (Gitlab) Drive re-use and leverage across Global Customer Success Team Transformation Office Look for opportunities to drive patents on business methods, services, and intellectual property Partner with Services PLM to drive standard repeatable service / service components to streamline sales and delivery About You: Minimum Qualifications BS degree in Computer Science, similar technical field of study Technology Strategy Architecture CMM/CMMI Solid Understanding of Six Sigma Leading development of repeatable service offerings / standardization Preferred Qualifications Master\u2019s or PhD degree Further education or experience in engineering, operations, and IT delivery About Ciena Ciena is a network strategy and technology company with a passion to provide an experience, to you and our customers that is as rewarding as the outcome. We attract the best and brightest\u2013 those with outstanding talent, motivation, and the right attitude to contribute to our success. Our culture balances our openness and informality with professionalism and trust and is built on the foundation of our core values: Customer First, Integrity, Velocity, Innovation, and Outstanding People. Ciena enables everyone to have a voice and a network that supports them while on the journey to discovering their passion and purpose. We trust each individual to do w